Lore - CHATGPT IDEA
In the distant future, Earth's resources are nearly depleted. Humanity seeks new planets to sustain life. During an
expedition, a lone human engineer crash-lands on Verdantia, a lush, vibrant world teeming with unique flora. This planet
is alive, and its plants, led by Verdant Guardians, fiercely protect their home. The engineer must gather data to
develop rockets for the journey back to Earth. Using skills to manufacture ammo and build turrets, the engineer
defends their base against relentless plant attacks, aiming to escape and save humanity.

Planet - VERDANTIA

Name - BOTANICAL BLITZ